data.description: Freshly Renovated Turn-Key Home is Ready for You! Or invest as rental income real estate, previous rental income of $2000 per month. Conveniently located near grocery stores and local business. The property has been extensively and thoughtfully renovated from top to bottom, making it a no projects needed home. Open Concept Living with a Large Primary Suite and Private 3/4 Bath. Just move in and make home! From the Double Pane Storm Windows, Updates on Plumbing, Cadet Heating, Fresh Paint, Laminate Plank Flooring, Updated Kitchen & Bathrooms, Electric Panel & Service, to Bonus potential in an unfinished upper level. Property has Alley Access and Off Street Parking.
